body:
https://k8s-gubernator.appspot.com/builds/kubernetes-jenkins/logs/ci-kubernetes-e2e-gce-reboot?before=8374

Judging by the timestamp, it's this batch of merge caused the failure:
```
commit fb4f44dca60d7ab29377927b1f2ada71da6c46bd
Merge: 17f0918bb9 6554dfc445
Author: Kubernetes Submit Queue <k8s-merge-robot@users.noreply.github.com>
Date:   Sat Jun 3 18:30:46 2017 -0700

    Merge pull request #46751 from liggitt/sni-cert-test
    
    Automatic merge from submit-queue (batch tested with PRs 40760, 46706, 46783, 46742, 46751)
    
    Pre-generate SNI test certs
    
    Pre-generates test certs for SNI tests, since doing this dynamically can take a loooong time in entropy-starved or CPU-bound test envs (like in a container).

commit 17f0918bb9f389f92427494d342bac22efea890b
Merge: 638c7382ae 902c501595
Author: Kubernetes Submit Queue <k8s-merge-robot@users.noreply.github.com>
Date:   Sat Jun 3 18:30:44 2017 -0700

    Merge pull request #46742 from caesarxuchao/update-gengo
    
    Automatic merge from submit-queue (batch tested with PRs 40760, 46706, 46783, 46742, 46751)
    
    Update gengo to the latest

commit 638c7382aec28ad2c711abc242e1e937e7312483
Merge: 64a4d23af2 475916cc59
Author: Kubernetes Submit Queue <k8s-merge-robot@users.noreply.github.com>
Date:   Sat Jun 3 18:30:42 2017 -0700

    Merge pull request #46783 from deads2k/controller-08-initfn
    
    Automatic merge from submit-queue (batch tested with PRs 40760, 46706, 46783, 46742, 46751)
    
    complete the controller context for init funcs
    
    This completes the conversion to initFuncs for the controller initialization to make easier and more manageable to add them.

commit 64a4d23af254bc932da3272d703735a2c10320e0
Merge: 4c7e1590ee a5865cfa1d
Author: Kubernetes Submit Queue <k8s-merge-robot@users.noreply.github.com>
Date:   Sat Jun 3 18:30:40 2017 -0700

    Merge pull request #46706 from CaoShuFeng/unit-create-role
    
    Automatic merge from submit-queue (batch tested with PRs 40760, 46706, 46783, 46742, 46751)
    
    Fix unit test for kubectl create role
    
    When expected err is not nil but error deos not happen, we should report error in unit test.
    **Release note**:
    
    ```
    NONE
    ```

commit 4c7e1590ee9ffcaa7133b1567a0bda42384db46b
Merge: dbd1503b65 f533bf729f
Author: Kubernetes Submit Queue <k8s-merge-robot@users.noreply.github.com>
Date:   Sat Jun 3 18:30:38 2017 -0700

    Merge pull request #40760 from mikedanese/gce
    
    Automatic merge from submit-queue (batch tested with PRs 40760, 46706, 46783, 46742, 46751)
    
    enable kubelet csr bootstrap in GCE/GKE
    
    @jcbsmpsn @pipejakob
    
    Fixes https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/issues/31168
```
